OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMadrid City Hall apologises
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover blackface videos      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Madrid's city hall has apologised after
OL,6, distributing videos featuring a white  
OL,7, actor wearing blackface as part of     
OL,8, wildly popular Epiphany festivities.   
OL,10,FOne of the videos also had the man in  
OL,11,Fblackface speaking in a heavy accent - 
OL,12,Fleading to accusations of racism.      
OL,14,FMadrid's deputy mayor apologised for   
OL,15,Fthe "regrettable mistake", blaming the 
OL,16,Fcompany which produced the videos.     
OL,18,FBlackface was a historical practice in 
OL,19,Fwhich black people were mocked for the 
OL,20,Fentertainment of white people.         
